	initialize: function() {

			var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
			r.setRequestBody(currentRecord.getValue('request_body'));
			r.setEndpoint(currentRecord.getValue('request_endpoint'));
			r.setHttpMethod('POST');
		
			var response = r.execute();
			var responseBody = response.getBody();
			var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
			
			currentRecord.response_body = responseBody;
			currentRecord.http_status = httpStatus;
			currentRecord.update();
		}
		catch(ex) {
			var message = ex.message;
		}
	},
	
	type: 'xM_Rest_Util'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-06 17:29:58</sys_created_on><sys_id>068b4d99dbc0330098bf85184b961930</sys_id><sys_mod_count>8</sys_mod_count><sys_name>xM_REST_Util</sys_name><sys_package display_value="xM Linc" source="x_273338_xm_linc">b5074119dbc0330098bf85184b961935</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="xM Linc">b5074119dbc0330098bf85184b961935</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_068b4d99dbc0330098bf85184b961930</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-26 18:05:03</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_273338_xm_linc.Data_Handler_Util</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description>This script include is called from the business rule (or rules) that live on the trigger table (source) of the alert. It takes the record in question (flat record only, all display values) and processes it by querying the condition table, if the record passes the condition (or conditions) it will be packaged and loaded into the outbound queue table. </description><name>Data_Handler_Util</name><script><![CDATA[var Data_Handler_Util = Class.create();
Data_Handler_Util.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},
	
	processRecord: function(recordToCheck) {
		var conditionGR = new GlideRecord('x_273338_xm_linc_condition_rules');
		conditionGR.addQuery('table', recordToCheck.getTableName());
		conditionGR.addQuery('active', 'true');
		conditionGR.query();
		
		if (conditionGR.hasNext()) {
			while (conditionGR.next()) {
				if (GlideFilter.checkRecord(recordToCheck, conditionGR.trigger_rule)) {
					this.buildPayload(recordToCheck, conditionGR);
				}
			}
		}
	},
	
	buildPayload: function(recordToSend, conditionRecord) {
		var outboundData = {};
			for (var prop in recordToSend) {
				if (prop != 'sys_meta') {
					outboundData[prop] = recordToSend.getDisplayValue(prop);
				}
			}
			var jsonOutboundData = JSON.stringify(outboundData);
			var outboundQueueGR = new GlideRecord('x_273338_xm_linc_outbound_queue');
			outboundQueueGR.initialize();
			outboundQueueGR.request_body = jsonOutboundData;
			outboundQueueGR.request_endpoint = conditionRecord.getDisplayValue('endpoint');
			outboundQueueGR.insert();
		},
		
		type: 'Data_Handler_Util'
};
	
	]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-06 17:29:35</sys_created_on><sys_id>266b0d99dbc0330098bf85184b9619a0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>6</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Data_Handler_Util</sys_name><sys_package display_value="xM Linc" source="x_273338_xm_linc">b5074119dbc0330098bf85184b961935</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="xM Linc">b5074119dbc0330098bf85184b961935</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_266b0d99dbc0330098bf85184b9619a0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-26 17:40:58</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
